channel.title: Boy Girl Dog Cat Mouse Cheese
channel.desc: Mouse discovers that Dog is able to make a sad puppy dog that allows him to get whatever he wants. When Mouse asks Dog to use this trick to get the Professor to loan him a special rare rock for his experiment, Dog refuses. To get his own back, Mouse uses a special invention that allows him to impersonate Dog and get the rock. What happens next is absolute mayhem.
